                <div class="rvt-card rvt-card--raised">
                    <div class="rvt-card__body">
                        <span class="rvt-ts-18 rvt-text-bold">Find your calling</span>
                        <p>IU offers more than 2,300 different programs of study. Not sure what to focus on? No problem. Browse by interest area to find options you'd enjoy pursuing.</p>
                        <a href="#0" class="rvt-cta">Browse degrees and majors</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
